  levelNumber: 2
  levelName: "Dzibilchalt\xFAn"
  location: Yucatan, Mexico
  levelDescription: "City of Light and Knowledge\n\nAncient even among Maya cities,
    Dzibilchalt\xFAn was a center of scholars and trade.\n\nHighlights\nTemple of
    the Seven Dolls: Aligns with the equinox sunrise, illuminating its doorways.\nTrade
    Hub: Connected the coast and inland cities for over 2,000 years, moving salt
    and obsidian.\nSacred Cenote: Provided fresh water and served as a spiritual
    gateway.\n\nLegacy\nShaped later by Spanish influence, the city still reflects
    a world of ritual, learning, and cosmic order\u2014renewed each equinox when
    sunlight passes through the temple\u2019s \u201Ceyes.\u201D"
